title: .net Magazine - June 2012 (.PDF)
description: Net Magazine is a great modern magazine which provides a complete guide to the internet. It aims to help businesses get better established and is ideal for businesses looking to get into the wider internet community and drive sales to your site or service. Net magazine aims to equip readers with the knowledge to get more confident when using the internet as well as being a useful tool for web designers who are already established in the sector.
